   &lt;tr&gt; 
    &lt;td&gt; &lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;**This part is not visible to students**&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;As a minimum, the Learning Materials section should include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
     &lt;ul&gt; 
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; A brief, informative introduction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Content arranged in folders based on Session or&amp;nbsp;Topic&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
     &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/td&gt; 
   &lt;/tr&gt; 
